It's already two years ago since we released the fourth edition of the 'Pure Salinas' compilation, so we are more than proud to bring you the 5th part now. Pure Salinas brings you the pure Ibiza Feeling. Relaxed, very danceable deep house sound that puts you into a laidback Balearic mood. The release is mixed and compiled by the Ibiza institution DJ Zappi and features the who-is-who of the deep house scene. On the first part are tracks by artists like Jon Sine, KANT, Fly O Tech and Dan Caster. Furthermore tracks and remixes by Sasha Breamer, Zoo Brazil, Sasse, Claptone, Kyodai and Stee Downes are on board. Part 2 keeps the luxury music taste. Zappi mixes songs & remixes by artists like Nolan feat. Amber Jolene, Dusky, Monkey Safari, Mikalogic and many others big names. The hit 'Lovebreak' by Milan Euringer and Tube & Berger, as well as more tracks and remixes by Antonio Olivieri, Rampue and Beatamines. No matter if you are chilling on the beach, lounging, or dancing in your head - feel the vibe of Pure Salinas.
